thread.title_full: Omega Rental Cars reviewed by Tourists

author: Tourists
title: Tourists
text: Unfortunately our plane arrived out of hours and we had difficulty finding where the car was parked at the airport especially in the drizzle and darkness that epitomises Wellington. It was quite awkward. But that aside we'd be hard pressed to find any other fault. The cars we have used have been spot on. Very comfortable and economical in fuel intake. Despite the earlier difficulty we would have no hesitation what-so ever of recommending this company.
